sentences: Pyotr Meshchaninov (1944 – 2006) was a Russian pianist and conductor specialized in Russian contemporary music.
He premiered Sofia Gubaidulina's Concerto for bassoon and low strings back in 1976, and was dedicated her 1981 Descensio.
